00:34:09.510 --> 00:34:12.530
In particular, it's a MathML
tree representation.

00:34:12.530 --> 00:34:17.540
And this representation is
recursively being traversed.

00:34:17.540 --> 00:34:20.889
And in every node,
an applicable

00:34:20.889 --> 00:34:23.750
rule is being computed.

00:34:23.750 --> 00:34:28.090
And that rule then has some
actions which fire, in the

00:34:28.090 --> 00:34:33.530
sense that they produce some
speech output, as well as

00:34:33.530 --> 00:34:37.810
produce a way to further
recursively traverse the rest

00:34:37.810 --> 00:34:39.870
of the tree.

00:34:39.870 --> 00:34:45.030
And these rules can be
customized in various ways.

00:34:45.030 --> 00:34:48.429
One way of customizing them is
customizing them with respect

00:34:48.429 --> 00:34:50.080
to mathematical domain.

00:34:50.080 --> 00:34:53.489
So what might be useful in one
mathematical domain might not

00:34:53.489 --> 00:34:55.710
be the same in another
mathematical domain.

00:34:55.710 --> 00:34:58.130
And when I say "mathematical
domain," what I actually mean

00:34:58.130 --> 00:35:04.290
is something like algebra,
geometry, analysis, calculus,

00:35:04.290 --> 00:35:05.610
things like this.

00:35:05.610 --> 00:35:09.550
So you might want to pronounce
one expression, in algebra,

00:35:09.550 --> 00:35:13.130
differently than in geometry.

00:35:13.130 --> 00:35:16.860
In addition to this, we have
the possibilities of

00:35:16.860 --> 00:35:19.210
customizing rules
by their style.

00:35:19.210 --> 00:35:22.760
And when I say "style" here, I
mean something like, do I want

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:25.010
it to be spoken short.

00:35:25.010 --> 00:35:28.450
Do I want it to be spoken in a
verbose mode, for instance.

00:35:28.450 --> 00:35:31.710
Do I want it to be spoken in
some particular way that I

00:35:31.710 --> 00:35:35.510
like, and nobody else
likes, et cetera.

00:35:35.510 --> 00:35:40.570
And finally, we also have the
possibility of swapping the

00:35:40.570 --> 00:35:47.610
underlying representation
while the

00:35:47.610 --> 00:35:48.870
speech engine is active.

